  "title": "Savory Korean Tofu Stew with Vanilla",
  "description": "A creamy, umami-packed Korean tofu stew that balances savory flavors with a hint of vanilla for depth, braised to perfection and suitable for Ayurvedic‑Rajasic diets.",
  "cuisine": "Korean",
